      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MADE BY MIA (5) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 0.8 lengths (21.01) at Nowra. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. MAGIC I AM (8) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at this track over 350m behind Rosabelle Mary (20.39) in a Grade 5. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has the ability to give this a shake. MORALE SPONGE (4) had been racing well prior to her last start eighth at Nowra following a Grade 5 win three back with a second placing. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break off the middle. Well placed here and can atone this time. ASTON JOE (7) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
